N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 1104.3 - Fees for reciprocal certificate and reciprocal license

State Regulations
(a) The application and renewal fee for a
reciprocal certificate shall be the same as the application fee for
certification established by section
160-f
of the

Executive Law. (b) The application
and renewal fee for a reciprocal license shall be the same as the application
fee for licensing established by section
160-f
of the

Executive Law. Notes
